            <title>東風 Forthing Friday SUV 登陸香港，多項安全配置 + 集舒適度與數碼體驗一身</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/dongfeng-forthing-friday-suv-launch/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dongfeng-forthing-friday-suv-launch</link>
